calc_bonus
Disk World creator help
calc_bonus

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
calc_bonus -  This method calculates the bonus for the skill.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int calc_bonus(int lvl,
string skill,
int use_base_stats)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^lvl%^RESET%^ - the level to turn into bonus
%^BOLD%^skill%^RESET%^ - the skill to modify the bonus of
%^BOLD%^use_base_stats%^RESET%^ - use the real unmodified stats
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the bonus associated with the skill
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/skills.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method calculates the bonus for the skill.  It takes the raw
level and turns that into a bonus and then adds on the stats
modifications.
.EP

